title: Can you help me please
body: Why we have not received summoner icon and frame for the end of season 6

replies.body: We're [currently experiencing some issues](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) with getting ranked rewards out to some players. We can assist you with these if you reach out in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) Let me know if you have any questions.
